    <p>{`To pass this schema back to express, we destructure import `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`GraphQLSchema`}</inlineCode>{` and at the bottom of the file we pass the root query.`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{}}>{`new GraphQLSchema({
    query: RootQuery
