`}</code></pre>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "the-graphiql-tool"
    }}>{`The Graphiql tool`}</h2>
    <p>{`This tool has been given to us by the GraphQL team. On the left hand side, we can write a query and run it to see what happens.`}</p>
    <p>{`The `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`docs`}</inlineCode>{` auto generates docs for us to see the type of queries we can make.`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{}}>{`// making the query
