    <p>{`We can now see the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`/companies`}</inlineCode>{` url can give us a company. To get JSON server to show us who works where, `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`json-server`}</inlineCode>{` works the relationship out at `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`companies/1/users`}</inlineCode>{`.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "updating-the-schema"
