    <p>{`Why can we get away with saying a related `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`company`}</inlineCode>{` and not `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`companyId`}</inlineCode>{`. Where the difference is, the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`resolve`}</inlineCode>{` function will help with the resolution.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "multiple-root-query-points"
    }}>{`Multiple Root Query Points`}</h2>
    <p>{`Currently, we cannot just find a company by itself. Only the user using the id.`}</p>
    <p>{`We can adjust this with adding to the Root Query.`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-javascript"
      }}>{`const RootQuery = new GraphQLObjectType({
