    <h3 {...{
      "id": "non-null-fields-and-mutations"
    }}>{`Non-null fields and Mutations`}</h3>
    <p>{`Given our application at the moment, it probably makes sense that all of these users we add with this mutation have a `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`firstName`}</inlineCode>{` and `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`age`}</inlineCode>{`. We can use `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`GraphQLNonNull`}</inlineCode>{` as a wrapper object to ensure the value is non-null.`}</p>
