`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`In opposition, `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`Relay`}</inlineCode>{` requires a bunch of configuration to start up and have a working provider.`}</p>
    <p>{`We can create a basic `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`SongList`}</inlineCode>{` component.`}</p>
